dataList.appIntro:
Let your stickers do the talking for you!
Instantly create your own funny cartoon stickers with AiMee and add a pinch of humor to your chats. In just 2 taps, you will have access to different sets of animated stickers using your face, for any emotion or situation. Just pick one, send it, and you’re guaranteed to surprise your friends and get questions asking how you did it! Our cartoon stickers add excitement to your daily conversations and help lighten the mood. 
How does it work?
1. Take a selfie, and….
2. Enjoy the stickers!
3. Change your sticker selection as you want 
Tip: If you want to access the keyboard please select it via your system settings. Then get to sharing stickers quickly and seamlessly via messaging apps. 
★ Why use AiMee : 
- Fast and easy access – Conveniently look for stickers while chatting. You can access all your stickers directly from your keyboard.
- Animated stickers that look just like you! With our advanced face recognition, stickers look very alive, and very much like you. 
- Quick share – Select a gif and share it with friends in just 2 taps. No need to jump to other apps, convert stickers to usable formats, save to your album and go through any trouble.
-  FREE stickers – Hundreds of free animated stickers made every day for you by our hard working creative design team. 
- Updated every day – Guaranteed delivery of new stickers every day and new sticker packs every week! You will never feel bored.
★ Pro Tips 
• Sign in with your MomentCam account (if you have made one before) to access all paid and favorite stickers that you had in MomentCam.
• Edit your face via the keyboard itself, just tap on the face edit icon in order to access a face that is already in use and tap once more to go to edit mode
• Add stickers to your Favorites to easily have access to them later!
• Add AiMee Keyboard via your settings and then select it from your system panel to start using AiMee’s keyboard services. 
• Animated stickers can only be shared on platforms that support gifs. Those apps are not under our control and we unfortunately cannot help if your stickers are sent as still images on them.
